{# ─── ABOUT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── #}
<section id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout fade-in">

      <div class="about-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading" id="about-heading">Cxbane</h2>
        <div class="rule"></div>
        <p class="body-text">
          Hey, I'm Vlad aka Cxbane. I'm based in Mannheim, Germany, and for as long as I can remember, art has been the thing that keeps me sane. Music and illustration aren't hobbies for me, they're outlets. Ways to process what's going on inside, to turn the darker, heavier stuff into something you can actually look at or listen to. My sound is stripped back but loaded. Dark atmospheres, honest words, minimal noise. And the visuals I create follow the same logic: nothing wasted, everything intentional.
        </p>
        <p class="body-text">
          There's a thread running through all of it: the need to make sense of what's in my head by putting it somewhere outside of it. If that resonates with you, you're in the right place.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://linktr.ee/cxbane"
          class="btn btn-outline"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >All Platforms</a>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual">
        <div class="about-image-frame">
          <img src="/assets/images/profile/cxbane.jpeg" alt="Cxbane" />
          <div class="frame-accent" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

